Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/radius-engine/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/radius-engine/radius-engine-1.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack radius-engine-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./radius-engine-1.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/radius-engine-1.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/radius-engine-1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libradius-engine1-1.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libradius-engine-devel-1.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(radius-engine)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/radius-engine.README
  /usr/share/doc/radius-engine/ChangeLog

(libradius-engine1)
  /usr/bin/cygradius-engine-1.dll

(libradius-engine-devel)
  /usr/include/radius.h
  /usr/lib/libradius-engine.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/radius-engine.pc

